{"tid":2344033,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"周子瑜才第4名！全球「百大美女」冠軍背景狂　僅19歲","createTime":"2020-12-28T11:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T19:31:53.000Z","uid":16659,"like":10,"dislike":269,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"945b5c4dadcf2e51a94f1a23070d0a8ea08e7861","tid":2344033,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T11:22:57.000Z","msg":"美國電影網站「TC Candler」每年都會評選全球知名的百大美女和百大帥哥，去年女明星排名的冠軍由南韓女團TWICE的台灣成員周子瑜拿下，2020名單今（28日）正式對外公布，可見這次子瑜滑到第四名，被第三名澳洲模特兒Meika Woollard、第二名是南韓女團BLACKPINK成員、泰國成員Lisa（Lalisa Manoban），以及第一名以色列超模Yael Shelbia打敗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/12/28/2328572-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F12%2F28%2F2328572-XXL.jpg&h=05efe7ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲周子瑜今年被排在第4名。（圖／翻攝自TWICE IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/26/2955261-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F26%2F2955261-PH.jpg&h=33877c18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這次獲得冠軍的Yael Shelbia（雅兒&middot;謝爾比亞），2001年出生於以色列納哈里亞，家人是正統的猶太家庭，16歲的時候雅兒在IG被發掘，並迅速成為時尚圈寵兒，只不過因為她的宗教背景，損失了不少模特兒合約，甚至引起女子猶太高中的反對，一度要寫信威脅以色列教育部將其開除，好在雅兒父母支持她的選擇，後來雅兒與以色列宗教教育部協商後，被允許在遵守某些規定的情況下，就能夠繼續學習。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/28/2957897-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F28%2F2957897-PH.jpg&h=e6ea9d37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲雅兒今年僅19歲。（圖／翻攝自Yael Shelbia IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/28/2957903-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F28%2F2957903-PH.jpg&h=160c0da1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雅兒陸續拍攝時尚大片，並在2019年參與首部電視劇演出，而她的美貌也很快被TC Candler列在百大美女臉孔裡，2017年獲得第17名，2018年被排在第3名，已經成了排名最高的以色列女星，力壓《神力女超人》蓋兒&middot;加朵（Gal Gadot），到了2019年更是直接躍升15個名次，位居亞軍位置，如今2020年的名單出爐，雅兒擠掉子瑜，成功拿下冠軍寶座，可見她在美貌、影響力、人氣等方面都非常厲害。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/28/2957895-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F28%2F2957895-PH.jpg&h=be8624f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲雅兒16歲出道，目前IG累積90萬人追蹤。（圖／翻攝自Yael Shelbia IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/28/2957896-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F28%2F2957896-PH.jpg&h=276442f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTC Candler每年都會評出「全球百大美女」以及「全球百大帥哥」，之後陸續有其他媒體效仿，但許多人還是認為TC Candler才是「真」榜單，此次百大美女前三是Yael Shelbia、Lisa、Meika Woollard；男星部分，第三名澳洲男星「雷神」克里斯&middot;漢斯沃（Chris Hemsworth）、第二名韓團防彈少年團的V（金泰亨），冠軍是瑞典知名YouTuber、實況主「PewDiePie」謝爾伯格（Felix Kjellberg）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/09/23/2787506-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F09%2F23%2F2787506-PH.jpg&h=90d26607&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲BLACKPINK的Lisa今年獲得百大美女第二名。（圖／翻攝自Lisa IG）"},{"pid":"629fada4786ff049bc7da0c73552ea31fb0f60ec","tid":2344033,"uid":165368,"like":59,"dislike":2,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T11:24:42.000Z","msg":"不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"724ce8e95339de29fb03d778ba10f02fd6837a90","tid":2344033,"uid":204743,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T11:27:42.000Z","msg":"Dasha Taran <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8782467f9e7625db731e9e812c57ae3462742833","tid":2344033,"uid":308570,"like":4,"dislike":43,"score":-39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T11:32:47.000Z","msg":"冠軍正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4320c2462bfe4d0b30431bcbd724fbebb310cda1","tid":2344033,"uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8782467f9e7625db731e9e812c57ae3462742833","tid":23440